      "text": "（月ストの初ライブは大盛況だったが、二度目は）\n（空席が目立った。そして迎えた三度目のライブの日）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The first Moon Tempest live went great‚ but there were empty seats)\n(at the second one. And now at their third live…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.827535731717944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.857394737005233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "心配しなくても\n前回よりしっかりお客さん入ってるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t worry.\nThere’s a much bigger crowd than last time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.857302121321364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "――っ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7856486260891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
