    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nいつからいたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nWhen did you get here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "俺がいることにも\n気付かないほど考え事してたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were thinking so hard\nyou didn’t even notice me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.62145597045883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.19058670903508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.19058670903508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……そうですね、気にしてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you’re right. I was a bit worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.823920042368417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "前回のライブ、空席が目立ってたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were empty seats last live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.357253375701752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.72140294616684
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "前回も普通に考えれば、決して少なくはない\nみんなは確実にステップアップしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not enough to be concerned.\nYou’re all doing well. Constantly improving.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.75473627950018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そうでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.40338475405192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、もっと自信を持ってほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. You should be more confident in yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.79531217514491,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.07517600952601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "あの……えっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ um…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.07517600952601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n正直に答えてほしいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nCan you tell me something? Be honest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.13302184044337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.619980532609766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは、こんな風にファンの入りを\n気にしてたことありましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did my sister ever worry like this\nabout how many fans she brought in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（なかった。でもそれを今言えば）\n（琴乃はさらに気にするかもしれない……どうする？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(No. But if I tell Kotono that now‚)\n(It might make her worry even more. What to do?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.147253178964654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.57836193590047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is something the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.57836193590047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……麻奈も、あったような\nなかったような……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I think maybe Mana did? Maybe?\nMaybe not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.40616238066238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.20167203277282
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私\n正直に言ってほしいって言いましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san.\nI asked you to be honest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3683386994395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.96771326997006
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "あいまいなのは嫌いです\n本当のことを言ってください",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hate vague answers.\nTell me the truth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.76771326997007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈はそんなこと\n一度も気にしてなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mana never worried about that.\nNot once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5010466033034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.40104660330339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "いつも満席だったからですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because she always sold out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.40104660330339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ。そもそも麻奈は\nそんなこと、考えすらしなかったと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. I think Mana just\nnever even thought about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.97993548848355,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.64660215515022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "考えないって……\nどういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She didn’t think about it?\nWhat do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.71925650164485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は、たとえお客さんが一人だけでも\nその人のために、全力で歌ったと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The audience could have been one person‚\nand Mana would have sung her heart out for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.718455690131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.50590573122074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.17257239788738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_01_02-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "……お姉ちゃんらしいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That sounds like something she’d do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.17257239788738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.11862685650554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
